These scripts were written by Lian.

1) get_window_id.sh: It will get the window id of the bash window playing music, and store it into the file_window_id file.
2) play_pause.sh: Play and pause.
3) prev_next_sh: Previous or next song.
4) stop.sh: Stop playing.
5) rm_file_window_id.sh: Remove the window id file file_window_id.
